{"tid":2017016,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譴責中國黑客企圖竊取武肺研究數據 美國務卿蓬佩奧：中共破壞行動的延續","createTime":"2020-05-15T00:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T00:16:22.000Z","uid":70063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b04053da8ce2135ae6ac4e16dc0e7c37e6c984e","tid":2017016,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1260973186532999170?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1260973186532999170%3Fs%3D19&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQ3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=5db76a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1260973186532999170%3Fs%3D19&h=94486d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1260973186532999170?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧周四發表聲明，譴責與中國有關的「網客和非傳統的資訊收集者」，企圖竊取美國有關武漢肺炎病毒研究的知識產權和數據。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說：「中共在網絡上的行為，正是他們在整個2019新冠病毒(COVID-19)疫情中的破壞行動的延續。當美國及盟友同心協力地採取共同而具透明度措施拯救生命時，中共卻繼續要科學家、記者和人民噤聲，又散播虛假消息，令這場公共衞生危機險上加險。」<br />\n<br />\n在蓬佩奧發表聲明前一天，美國聯邦調查局（FBI）和國土安全部發表聯合聲明，警告有中國黑客試圖入侵美國醫學研究機構，收集與武漢肺炎病毒有關的研究資料和數據。聲明沒有透露黑客與目標機構的詳情，中國駐美大使館否認指控，指是「謊言」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200515/YIK5RU5FBOI5PP4EMW2PGOJSAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200515%2FYIK5RU5FBOI5PP4EMW2PGOJSAM%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQ3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=1ac043ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200515%2FYIK5RU5FBOI5PP4EMW2PGOJSAM%2F&h=b5b85243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200515/YIK5RU5FBOI5PP4EMW2PGOJSAM/</a>"}]}